metadata.description:
This is a collaboration between artists, developers, and passionate people who want to help Ukraine in this time of need.

 100% of the proceeds will go to Ukrainian funds like [ComeBackAlive](https://www.comebackalive.in.ua/) that provide humanitarian relief to the people of Ukraine and the Ukrainian army.

Visit us at https://www.istandwithukraine.love/ to learn more.

NFT design by [Victoria Wardia](https://www.instagram.com/vwardia/)

Thank you so much for being a part of this cause and supporting Ukraine!
metadata.name: IStandWithUkraine
